//Use this expression to automate the creation of LEVEL_ID values using attribute rules in ArcGIS Pro.
//The following comments are for describing how to set up the attribute rules.
//Set description to "This attribute rule updates the LEVEL_ID for feature classes based on the items Facility ID and Floor Level."
//Set Subtype to <ALL>
//Set Field to LEVEL_ID
//Set Editable to Yes.
//The below comments until the last comment are for use in the expression itself.
//Concatenate the Facility ID and the Floor Level.
$feature.FACILITY_ID+ "_F"+$feature.NAME_SHORT[0]
//Set Triggers to Insert and Update.
